Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她进来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是瑞穗家的千金 渡边早季小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必这么拘束哦
